VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \breinterpret_cast<[^>]+>\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:static_assert|static_cast|bit_cast|is_trivially_copyable
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of `reinterpret_cast`, which can lead to unsafe type conversions.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Unsafe Type Conversion: reinterpret_cast.
